{"tid":2463487,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"網紅為 1.6 萬港元賞金 喪吞 4 大包鹽","createTime":"2021-03-26T17:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T19:34:18.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1105847ba9a0845ff5da48768e31807fc4fc945b","tid":2463487,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915656/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2915656%2F1_1024.jpg&h=32d0cf1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據外國媒體報道，網紅 anggun 常分享自己狂吃美食的影片，他還很能吃辣，單吃一盤辣椒都沒問題，許多網民好奇他的飲食極限可以到哪。日前 anggun 就收到一名網民的要求，只要他吞掉 4 包鹽，成功的話他就可以獲得 3,000 萬印尼盾。<br />\n<br />\n想不到 anggun 果然按對方的要求，拍片吃鹽。他先將 4 包鹽倒進盤子，接著拿起湯匙，一口一口吞起來，過程中他還用手抓鹽起來吃，中途好像有點難受。最後他順利完成挑戰，拿起一旁的鈔票展示。<br />\n<br />\n這段影片上傳至今吸引 150 萬人次按讚，觀看人次更突破 2,000 萬大關。有網民表示：「小心腎衰竭啊」、「用腎臟換獎金？」、「出錢的人和你有仇吧」、「有錢沒命花，健康才是真正的財富」。另外，也有網民質疑影片造假，認為他吞下的根本不是鹽，而是換成了其他東西。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915656/md-02f044f6bbc3815818ec1acf36fb8fd0_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2915656%2Fmd-02f044f6bbc3815818ec1acf36fb8fd0_600.jpg&h=58707a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915656/NARWsRBlfgdFYwqLDv7F-1C-PwkOo1RCGqKLVRqii1U_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2915656%2FNARWsRBlfgdFYwqLDv7F-1C-PwkOo1RCGqKLVRqii1U_600.jpg&h=da22682b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2915656/gtGYnO5IZ8T-yJ8wcGiKV-koWq5seC0X_SzID_0syA8_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt